{"tid":1228565,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人情緒急救方法","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T22:07:29.000Z","uid":3273,"like":56,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"32297ce09cf49dc7d59d9028d3b7eaa97d84a116","tid":1228565,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:24:16.000Z","msg":"學過幾個方法面對突發情緒<br />\n分享個我覺得最有用嘅<br />\n<br />\n深呼吸，合埋眼，左手放係手口<br />\n感受下自己手掌嘅溫度<br />\n<br />\n平伏左之後，諗住有個氣球，揀隻自己鍾意嘅顏色<br />\n將所有唔開心，負面情緒吹晒入去<br />\n鼻吸口呼，吹晒入個氣球到<br />\n<br />\n覺得差唔多就可以打返個結，將個氣球放手<br />\n望住佢一路飛走，個氣球愈黎愈遠，愈黎愈細<br />\n遠到睇唔到，細到唔見左。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第二個方法<br />\n<br />\n沖涼嘅時候，用花撒由頭淋到腳<br />\n感受下清澈潔淨嘅水流過自己皮膚嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n將所有唔開心嘅事情、感覺、情緒<br />\n係自己心口釋放出黎<br />\n水流會將你所有唔開心嘅事情、感覺、情緒<br />\n全部都沖走<br />\n流晒落坑渠沖走晒<br />\n<br />\n重複直到自己覺得舒服返<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位加油<br />\n香港仲要靠大家<br />\n聽日見！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不撤不散！</span>"},{"pid":"7e460f198d1d2263d9934991950287bdd8d55f2d","tid":1228565,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:25:14.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f63abc0e15c5e6d90c07bd351973485c688d5297","tid":1228565,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:27:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40860b3d99eff3b297bd9bff139c0731b9c27a0d","tid":1228565,"uid":185092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:27:53.000Z","msg":"YouTube search靜觀練習"},{"pid":"44383035aca233c94cfc386fa9ea7d159b122aa0","tid":1228565,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:29:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"873104dac85573c48d883c7fca4b926aa4287014","tid":1228565,"uid":3273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:30:17.000Z","msg":"10<img src=\"